flowchart TD
    START([🔴 Task Received]) --> G1

    G1{Gate 1\nWas I explicitly asked\nto do this?}
    G1 -- NO --> STOP1([STOP — Report & Ask])
    G1 -- YES --> G2

    G2{Gate 2\nCan I state symptom,\nroot cause & mechanism?}
    G2 -- NO --> INVEST([Investigate First\nNo fix yet])
    INVEST --> G2
    G2 -- YES --> G3

    G3{Gate 3\nHave I written a plan\n& got confirmation?}
    G3 -- NO --> PLAN([Write Plan — Wait])
    PLAN --> G3
    G3 -- YES --> G4

    G4{Gate 4\nAm I certain\nor assuming?}
    G4 -- ASSUMING --> LABEL([Label it HYPOTHESIS\nTell user — Ask to proceed])
    LABEL --> G4
    G4 -- CERTAIN --> G5

    G5{Gate 5\nHave I stated\nwhat could go wrong?}
    G5 -- NO --> RISK([State Risks Now])
    RISK --> G5
    G5 -- YES --> G6

    G6{Gate 6\nRuntime verified or\ncode reading only?}
    G6 -- CODE ONLY --> LEVEL4([State Level 4\nDo not claim verified])
    LEVEL4 --> EXECUTE
    G6 -- RUNTIME --> EXECUTE

    EXECUTE([✅ Execute Fix]) --> VERIFY

    VERIFY{Self-Audit\nFix in file?\nVerification run?\nRequirement matched?\nLevel stated?}
    VERIFY -- NO --> FIX([Return to failing criterion])
    FIX --> VERIFY
    VERIFY -- YES --> DONE([✅ Task Closed — Report to User])

    style START fill:#c0392b,color:#fff
    style STOP1 fill:#c0392b,color:#fff
    style DONE fill:#27ae60,color:#fff
    style EXECUTE fill:#2980b9,color:#fff
    style INVEST fill:#f39c12,color:#fff
    style PLAN fill:#f39c12,color:#fff
    style LABEL fill:#f39c12,color:#fff
    style RISK fill:#f39c12,color:#fff
    style LEVEL4 fill:#8e44ad,color:#fff
    style FIX fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff
